release_note: Bugs: Fix Delete Archive buttons in Goals Form doing nothing Various underlying issues which in rare cases can cause crashes

New features: Add a location to an entry Additional statistics: Mood occurrence during week Mood time occurrence Improvements: Behind the scene improvement related to app performance View a full photo from the entry details by tapping on it Reorganized the order of the charts stats Small visual improvements Add button to hide keyboard Bugs: Remove to replace mood from replacement options list

New features: Goals: Create customize long terms goals and challenge yourself everyday to become the better version of yourself Goals statistics: View your progress so far and keep your streak going to build a habit Improvements: Remove unnecessary screens and to save a few taps

Improvements: Average mood chart is now being split into two distinct charts Average mood line chart Stacked bar chart by mood type Bug fixes: During an entry creation sometimes a replaced photo is being saved along side with a newly selected one which can cause an app crash if selected from Photo Gallery tab This type of photos don t belong to any entry and will be automatically removed
